'''Gary Glitter''' is a hilarious [[British]] pedophile glam rocker known for hits such as [[Football|Rock and Roll Part 2]], [[Unwarranted_Self-Importance|Leader Of The Gang]] and [[Asking For It|Do You Wanna Touch]], who was convicted of sex offenses [[fail|twice]], once in 1999 for downloading child porn images, and then in 2005 for raping some [[loli]] in [[shithole|Vietnam]].
[[Image:Garyglitter2.jpg|thumb|right|Gary In His Prime.]]
==Music==
[[Glitter]] started his career in the early [[Old|70s]] jumping on the Glam Rock bandwagon that David Bowie and Marc Bolan started, Imagine Elvis Presley drunk and high on [[LSD]] stuck in a tinfoil factory and you'll get the picture. Most of Glitter's music consists of shouting [[cum|COME ON COME ON]] and [[gay|HEY]] and some [[obvious|subtle]] pedo references, his music never really reached the US, except the song 'Rock And Roll Part 2', which is played at <strike>[[steroids|American Football]] events</strike> EVERY fucking sporting event (including high school), since [[redneck|Americans]] are too stupid to notice a fucking pedo made the song. For some reason people put up with his shit through the 80s and early 90s and had appearances on [[pedo|kids shows]], he was also going to be in the Spice Girls movie, although Gary's appearance [[Bullshit|would have probably won the film an Oscar]].
[[Image:Garydrugs.jpg|thumb|right|Glitter was also known to be a crackhead.]]

==Pedophilia==
Being the horny prat he is, Gazza downloaded [[over 9000]] child porn images, some featuring [[jailbait|kids]] as young as [[too old|2]], when his piece of shit computer broke [[asking for it|he sent his computer to PC World]], being the nosey little fucks that they are, they snooped around the pedo's computer and found a goldmine of kiddy porn, Glitter was eventually found guilty, served his time in jail and said he [[lies|deeply regrets what he done]] and wants to put it all behind him, so the crusty old pedo went to various places including Cuba, Spain and eventually Vietnam. Being the easiest place to get underage sex in the world, Glitter was asking for trouble and should have gave up while he was ahead, but in 2005 the papers started going ape shit again as the bald old glitterman was touching [[loli]]s in [[azn|Vietnam]].

==Glitter Explains Himself==
In an interview, Gary tried to make up a half assed story about the girl he slept with being scared of ghosts and [[Wut|mosquito nets]], but ended up being interrupted by a bitchy reporter.

He should have just admitted it and got therapy.

==IRL Trolling==
British newspaper tabloids such as [[boobs|The Sun]] and the [[Lies|News Of The World]], have taken it to the streets trying to catch all his crazy disguises to avoid being seen, ranging from a [[Rofl|Rolf]] Harris style wig and beard to a ginger wig and straw hat.
It as been thought that Gary wears a [[pedobear|bear costume]] to [[Partyvan|children's parties]].

